Figure_title: Figure 4. Baseline and on-study brain MRI images for a patient with SQSTM1-NTRK1- rearranged lung cancer Baseline head CT scans show metastases (red arrows) in the left occipital lobe (top panel)  and in the right thalamus (bottom panel). Restaging head CT scans show complete response  at 1 month and 18 months on entrectinib (at the time of data cutoff).
